ğŸ’° FLS â€” Financial Logic Shield (Public Demo)

Proteksi logika finansial berbasis aturan.

Tujuan:

mencegah nilai tidak valid

membatasi reward demo

menyaring aksi berisiko


// demo-only (placeholder)
export function evaluate(action){
  if (action.amount <= 0) return { allowed: false, reason: "invalid_demo" };
  if (action.type === "reward" && action.amount > DEMO_LIMIT)
    return { allowed: false, reason: "reward_limit_demo" };
  return { allowed: true };
}


