ğŸ™ï¸ CES â€” City Engagement System (Public Demo)

Mendeteksi mood kota berdasarkan jenis aksi user:

export function evaluateMood(action){
  if (action.type === "help") return { mood: "positive" };
  if (action.type === "spam") return { mood: "alert" };
  return { mood: "neutral" };
}

Contoh output:

positive â†’ dukungan warga

alert â†’ potensi gangguan

neutral â†’ normal



---

ğŸ‘® APS â€” AI Police System (Public Demo)

Layer proteksi perilaku:

export function scan(action, mood){
  if (mood.mood === "alert") return { status: "watch" };
  if (action.type === "spam") return { status: "warn" };
  if (action.type === "exploit") return { status: "block" };
  return { status: "clear" };
}

Tujuan:

cegah spam

deteksi eksploit

tandai anomali awal



---

ğŸ‘‘ AMS â€” AI Mayor System (Public Demo)

Menyesuaikan kebijakan global berdasarkan hasil APS:

export function adjustPolicy(action, police){
  if (police.status === "block")
    return { globalMood: "strict", note: "increased_security_demo" };
  if (action.type === "help")
    return { globalMood: "open", note: "citizen_support_demo" };
  return { globalMood: "stable" };
}


